OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fclear away this evening, then dry with
OL,7,Fclear periods for a time. Thickening
OL,8,Fcloud will bring rain across all parts
OL,9,Flater in the night. Freshening south
OL,10,Fto southwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FOvernight rain soon clearing
OL,13,Faway. Then drier with a few showers
OL,14,Ffor a time. Further rain will spread
OL,15,Fnortheast in the afternoon. Strong
OL,16,Fsouthwesterly winds in the afternoon.
OL,17,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
