OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FAny
OL,6,Fovernight rain soon clearing on Monday
OL,7,Fmorning, then mainly dry although some
OL,8,Fshowery rain possible in the west
OL,9,Flater. Dry on Tuesday and for most of
OL,10,FWednesday.
